OL,3,CHistoric wins for Green's in the
OL,4,Ccapital
OL,6,FFor the first time, the capital has
OL,7,Ftwo directly elected Green mayor's and
OL,8,Fcontrol of two London councils.
OL,10,FZoe Garbett won the former Labour
OL,11,Fstronghold of Hackney, and Liam
OL,12,FShivastava, a former Labour councillor
OL,13,Fbecame Lewisham's Green mayor.
OL,15,FThe Green's took Waltham Forest from
OL,16,FLabour before later taking Hackney.
OL,18,FThe parties success was a bruising
OL,19,Fdefeat for Labour.
OL,26,@rD@Cxr
