OL,3,CHistoric wins for Green's in the
OL,4,Ccapital
OL,6,FIn Hackney, some 42 Green councillors
OL,7,Fwere elected, and Labour lost 34 seats
OL,8,Fto hold on to just nine.
OL,10,FThe Conservatives maintained six seats
OL,11,Fon the council.
OL,13,FThe newly elected mayor of Hackney,
OL,14,FZoe Garbett vowed to "change the
OL,15,Fsystem".
OL,17,FSpeaking after the results, she said:
OL,19,F"Today we start a fightback. In this
OL,20,Felection, over and over, people kept
OL,21,Ftelling me that they felt let down.
OL,26,@vD@CxrvD@VOUwD@GO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778425867
OL,3,CHistoric wins for Green's in the
OL,4,Ccapital
OL,6,F"People kept saying, 'it's hard for me
OL,7,Fand it's hard for us'. Council
OL,8,Fservices are failing those who need
OL,9,Fthem most and people are struggling to
OL,10,Fmake ends meet.
OL,12,F"To everyone who voted for me, I truly
OL,13,Fthank you for putting your trust in me
OL,14,Ftoday."
OL,16,FThe borough had been under Labour
OL,17,Fcontrol since 2002.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
