OL,3,CHistoric wins for Green's in the
OL,4,Ccapital
OL,6,FWhen the Green's reached 29
OL,7,Fcouncillors and had secured a majority
OL,8,Fearlier on Friday, Green supporters
OL,9,Fchanted: "What colour is Hackney?
OL,10,FGreen."
OL,12,FZack Polanski spoke in Hackney
OL,13,Ffollowing the results. He said his
OL,14,Fmessage to Keir Starmer is "It's time
OL,15,Fto go."
OL,17,FThe Leader of the Green Party
OL,18,Fcontinued:
OL,26,@qD@JOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
