OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1778425867
OL,3,CHistoric wins for Green's in the
OL,4,Ccapital
OL,6,F"The country has clearly rejected you.
OL,7,FI think he'd been rejected before
OL,8,Fthese elections even started.
OL,10,F"We had 14 years of Conservative
OL,11,Fausterity.
OL,13,F"Keir Starmer was voted in on a
OL,14,Fpromise of change and, actually, what
OL,15,Fwe've seen is very little change, and
OL,16,Fin many ways things have got worse."
OL,18,FIn Lewisham, Liam Shrivastava took
OL,19,Fover from the previous Labour mayor,
OL,20,FBrenda Dacres.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
