OL,3,CHistoric wins for Green's in the
OL,4,Ccapital
OL,6,FThe victorious Green party candidate
OL,7,Fhad previously served as Labour party
OL,8,Fcouncillor before defecting to the
OL,9,FGreens last year.
OL,11,FIn a post on social media, Liam
OL,12,FShrivastava said "We made Lewisham
OL,13,Fgreen" and thanked those who supported
OL,14,Fhim throughout the local elections.
OL,16,FHe said that the Green party are
OL,17,F"Committed to bringing hope to
OL,18,FLewisham."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
